repastcity3.environment
Interface Cacheable

All Known Implementing Classes:
Route, SpatialIndexManager
public interface Cacheable

Used by any class which has static cached objects. Static caches must be cleared at the start of each simulation or they will persist over multiple simulation runs unless Simphony is restarted.
